data.description: Updated and ready to move in! Open 2 story great room! 4 bedroom plus a loft! Spacious master includes a luxury bath w/over sized tiled shower & walk in closet! Bright kitchen is updated with beautiful marble countertops, backsplash, soft close cabinets, large pantry & ss appliances! Super durable vinyl plank floors are easy to clean! Fireplace with ceramic logs! Blinds on many windows! Finished basement includes a large bedroom with stylish barn doors, full bath, wet bar & mini fridge, plenty of recreational area & new carpet! Under stair storage! Water softener rough-in, radon system  back up sump pump!  Fenced yard with paver patio & firepit!
